title: Applanet   Version 2.6.5.  Free Android Apps
description:
Version 2.6.5
Release date 22/1/11
Connection to new server,
Fixed a few bugs.


*Access Paid Apps for FREE!*

Applanet's massive database contains more than 9,000 Android applications. You have access the to latest version of both free and paid applications found in the Android Market and even some you can't and won't have to pay anything! Applanet is your one-stop 


*Familiar Interface*

Whether you are a power user or new to Android, Applanet has a familiar interface like the one found in the Android Market. You can view Apps, Games and which of your existing applications of updates available. 

Tested working fine
